  "texts": [
    "Moreover, Jovanovic and Rousseau (2005, p. 1185) show that the distinguishing characteristics of a GPT are:",
    "Qeios, CC-BY 4.0 • Article, February 29, 2024 Qeios ID: NR1YME • https://doi.org/10.32388/NR1YME 16/35",
    "Pervasiveness: A GPT should propagate to many sectors.",
    "Improvement: A GPT should reduce the costs of its adopters.",
    "A GPT should produce new products and processes (cf. also Bresnahan and Trajtenberg, 1995)."
  ]
